OL,3,CSinkhole on main road causing
OL,4,Cdisruption to businesses in Dumfries
OL,6,FAnnan Road in Dumfries remains closed
OL,7,Fafter a large sink hole emerged almost
OL,8,Ftwo weeks ago.JLocal businesses have
OL,9,Fsaid it's made the area much quieter
OL,10,Fas is affecting trade.
OL,12,FIt's one of the busiest routes in and
OL,13,Fout of Dumfries, and Scottish Water
OL,14,Fsaid it's 'too early to say' how long
OL,15,Fit's set to be closed for while
OL,16,Frepairs are carried out.
OL,18,FIt said the works could only be
OL,19,Fcarried out safely with a full road
OL,20,Fclosure, due to a damaged sewer about
OL,21,F4m (13ft) underground.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/3
