PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1781385841
OL,3,CSinkhole on main road causing
OL,4,Cdisruption to businesses in Dumfries
OL,6,FA spokesperson said, "We appreciate
OL,7,Fthis is a key route for people in
OL,8,FDumfries and everything will be done
OL,9,Fto minimise any disruption and to
OL,10,Fcomplete the work as quickly and
OL,11,Fsafely as possible," it said.
OL,13,F"It is too early to say how long the
OL,14,Froad closure will be in place, but we
OL,15,Fwill have a better idea once the
OL,16,Fdamaged sewer has been exposed and
OL,17,Fsurveyed.
OL,19,F"We would like to thank everyone
OL,20,Faffected for their patience and
OL,21,Funderstanding."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/3
